data.description:
Big News!!!   Seller is offering a $10,000.00 credit towards a rate buy down or closing costs.  You choose what would benefit you the most. 
Why not make a move to this gorgeous home on a cul-de-sac?  This home has had many updates including the addition of a 5th bedroom in the lower level which can be changed back into a family room, and an updated primary bed and bath.   You can enjoy a glass of ice tea on the front deck or choose one of the two decks on the back of your home that overlook a beautiful backyard.   Call today for a private showing.
